<p><b><a name="Blacksmithing:"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Blacksmithing:</font></a></b></p>
<ul>
  <li><font face="Verdana" size="2"><a href="http://www.everlore.com/guides.asp?ID=259466">Everlore's
